text: The 2009 Jayco Herald Sun Tour was the 58th edition of the Herald Sun Tour, a six-stage bicycle race held from 11–17 October 2009 in Victoria, Australia. The race was won by Bradley Wiggins, ahead of Chris Sutton and Jonathan Cantwell. ==References== Jayco Herald Sun Tour, 2009 Jayco Herald Sun Tour Category:UCI Oceania Tour races Category:Cycle races in Australia
